			"value": "<p>An familiar's blast mimics the @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.FHiTJvr5Nbb7HsgX]{Eldritch Blast} of their bonded @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class.Item.whbTNYgkqWV8oGt3]{warlock}.</p><p></p><p><span><strong>Familiar's Action</strong> </span>- 1 Creature* (120 ft.) - Cantrip (Evocation)- VS</p><p>Spell Attack (using the warlock's spell attack bonus)</p><ul><li><p>Hit: [[/r 1d4]] + the warlock's spellcasting ability modifier force damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p>A familiar's blast doesn't benefit from invocations that improve their warlock's @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.FHiTJvr5Nbb7HsgX]{Eldritch Blast}.</p>",
